2.4 Workstream Service
2.4.1 Authoritative Responsibilities & Operational Scope
* Tenant Authority: Authoritatively manages all workspace records in the Workstreams and WorkstreamMemberships tables in Ollie Spanner.
* Access Control Gatekeeper: Evaluates fine-grained permissions (VIEWER, EDITOR, ADMIN, AGENT_DELEGATOR) for human teammates and automated agent service accounts across all system actions.
* Asset Provisioning Engine: Binds, reconciles, and synchronizes external Google infrastructure (Google Groups, Shared Drives, Buganizer Hotlists, Jira projects, Chat spaces) to workstream workspaces.
