* PTY Watchdog & Hermetic Actuation: Commands execute inside a dedicated PTY supervisor process. If a command (e.g., raw grep across //depot/google3) hangs without emitting newline tokens for $>30$ seconds, the PTY watchdog injects SIGTERM, intercepts the failure, and returns an actionable error instruction guiding the agent to use code_search instead.
